                                    <span>Total</span>
                                </td>
                                <td colspan="4" style="border: 1px solid black;">
                                    <span t-field="doc.amount_total"/>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p>License Contract thru e-email</p>
                    <p>ALL Prices are in SA. Quoted prices are not valid in case of quantity or product change .</p>
                    <p>Technology Partners for Trading is not responsible for any Government Charges (Witholding TAX
